Installation Notes

InterTrax 2 USB event handler module

 - make
 - su 
 - make install
 - ./testtracker



"make install" will copy itrax.o to /lib/modules/misc and make "depmod".
If not found, the following device will be created:

crw-r--r--   1 root     root      13, 128 Nov 27 11:34 /dev/input/tracker0 

The minor devicenumber is not officaly assigned yet.

This module was tested with Linux 2.2.16 (SuSE) and 2.4.0.


